  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.boot.actuate.autoconfigure.cloudfoundry.reactive.ReactiveCloudFoundryActuatorAutoConfiguration

  • @Configuration(proxyBeanMethods=false)

                       matchIfMissing=true)
